author: @hiokeh
text:
from Sahara in 2019 to the main stage in 2023! BLACKPINK absolutely ate up this performance! From their stunning group performances to their solo performances- You and Me remix bringing out the powerful Jennie, Jisoo being extremely elegant during Flower, Rose being angelic and proving once again that she has such strong vocals and stage presence, and Lisa feeling herself during the explicit Money! 

The girls really pushed and proved themselves this performance. It’s really so emotional seeing them coming this far, headlining one of the biggest music events in the world. Blinks, let’s support and continue to give constructive criticism to BLACKPINK no matter what they do- be it them being in relationships or having controversies. Blackpink deserves to be loved and not obsessed over by toxic “fans”. BLACKPINK IS THE REVOLUTION! 🖤 🩷
